What is viral video? Here's a clue, it is
not a disease you get from watching TV.
It is... well, I had no idea what it was until this report.
Yo Taylor- Yo, yo, yo Taylor. I-I'm really happy for you.

I'ma let you finish. I'ma-I'ma let you finish.
I'ma
let you finish. I'ma-I'ma let you finish.

--one of the
best videos of all time --all time --all time.
Yo Taylor, I'ma let Beyonce let you finish.
Ah, Charlie, Charlie bit me-e-e-e
............Oooooow! Charlie! That really hurt!

Charlie bit me; Charlie bit me. (aaaay)
And that really hurt.

I heard it through the grapev-i-i-i-ne.
And I heard it through the great banana tree.
Ahaha! Give me your banana for a second. No!
Where were you Shawtayee?

Ummm... I was in the attic.
And went up there, my dad
yelled at me, he didn't want me to play in the flying saucer.
Why did not you come out when we called your name, Shawtayee?
You guys said that we did this for a show.
[retching noises]

Auto-Tune the puke. Auto-Tune the puke.
Auto-Tune the puke. Auto-Tune the puke.
You decide. Vote for the best unintentional singer in the comments.

Only you can choose: Does Kanye sound better on
purpose on his album, or by accident?

You have the power.
